title: Vita Sano Vegetarian Grocery
description: They make tofu, power soya, and have carrot juice w/ calamansi and celery. They supply soya and carrot juice to the gyms in Laguna area. They sell vegetarian frozen food but is limited to gluten, tapa and sausage only. Staff will recommend recipes for cooking the vegetarian foods. Delivery available. Previously named Vita Grazia Vegetarian Grocery.
streetAddress: B8 L16 Myna Road, Southdrive Village, Sta Rosa City
